Package: filetree
Title: Declarative File Tree Schemas and Validation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a 'filetree' object for declaring the expected 
    structure of a file hierarchy. A file listing can be parsed and 
    validated against the declared file tree to extract metadata and 
    identify structural and naming inconsistencies.
